{"tid":1597721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【南丫島沉船】10月1仲有一個港殤!!","createTime":"2019-09-27T05:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:03:14.000Z","uid":74888,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c56a0f06e68a2cc85c5fad8e0fab74a385769cc4","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"大家係發夢既同時, 唔好唔記得7年前既呢一件事<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2012年南丫島海難</strong><br />\n<br />\n2012年南丫島海難是於2012年10月1日在香港南丫島榕樹灣發生的一宗海難。一艘載有127人的港燈公司船隻準備前往欣賞國慶煙花途中，在南丫島對開海域被一艘港九小輪公司的雙體船攔腰撞擊，並於兩分鐘內沉沒，造成39人死亡。該宗海難為自1971年佛山輪海難之後，近41年來香港死亡人數最多的海難事故，也是繼2010年菲律賓人質事件後另一宗被視為「港殤」的事件。[1]<br />\n<br />\n是次事件引起不少網民熱烈討論，當中包括意外情況和原因、政府的種種善後措施，以至中聯辦懷疑介入事件和事發後緊接的國慶煙花應否取消等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2012%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E9%9B%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F2012%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%2597%25E4%25B8%25AB%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%259B%25A3&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=f29b868e\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2012%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E9%9B%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n而根據Wiki所講既意外發生時間為晚上8點23分<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%92%9E%E8%88%B9%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E4%25B8%25AB%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%2588%25B9%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=2b0b6ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%92%9E%E8%88%B9%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a><br />\n所以懇求大家出黎發夢既同時, 8點23分為呢班港殤既死難者默哀一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於默幾耐大家覺得呢?<br />\n我自己覺得由23分默到25分都OK<br />\n求下大家幫我推到文宣組見到, 先可以貼去連儂同spread出去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2999b3a67ee3cc2253f79af41c9647e3345a2f","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a2cfc1d927c7cef1edd09f74c732f61f6404cad9","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"21f003490519391d4fa4d718fe1715a654eb7aa0","tid":1597721,"uid":211645,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69554c4c4487a56a70c77c812acf902d4469935a","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21f003490519391d4fa4d718fe1715a654eb7aa0","tid":1597721,"uid":211645,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？<br />\n大家可以起下我底⋯"},{"pid":"8156189a84c4f2ef466415b0027c723a8dda9caf","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e0e6d8d8f967e8eb19f0f049fd4c35f73812e4e7","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f0fe7cea61465dacdb85bdb20ee4f2290ea25558","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5e4901fe6ba6aeb9e4ce386f14207e9d10018e9e","tid":1597721,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"60221bcc421d07c2f5e6fe19b1a05d7b0c0939ca","tid":1597721,"uid":200464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4bfb123f2070586b57207ed644635dbca75eda7f","tid":1597721,"uid":200464,"like":0,"dis